    "name": "FiMFiction.net - Custom User Toolbar Color",
    "description": "A simple little style to force a custom color scheme on the user toolbar.",
    "additionalInfo": "When using a light background, the button borders will be visible as a color-blended gray.\r\n\r\nI'd have implemented it for dark backgrounds too but something about the color-blending is being contrary.",
